{"tid":657432,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[純討論] 如果香港少左一半人口會唔會快樂好多","createTime":"2018-05-08T06:06:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-10T06:23:02.000Z","uid":54551,"like":91,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"5f8deda9de675d550ea0922ad9617c8c89a6fdda","tid":657432,"uid":54551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T06:06:55.000Z","msg":"啲人成日講到香港地壓力大，老實講咪又係因為競爭大<br />\n由出世爭床位, 去到爭小學中學大學, 爭政府工/工務員, 爭公屋居屋, 到死果秒都爭緊個位裝骨灰<br />\n<br />\n但如果少左一半人口會點？其實一直以嚟壓力嘅來源，都係人口....<br />\n<br />\n唔係話無辜嘅人都有罪，錯嘅都只會係發展得太快嘅社會.... 呢排睇完戲再諗翻起人口澎脹嘅個問題，香港如果少左一半人，可能競爭力會低左，但起碼唔會覺得香港係唔想居住嘅城市之一"},{"pid":"318bd3196c652680edd76646dc317c0b54ddc064","tid":657432,"uid":28831,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T06:09:52.000Z","msg":"會<br />\n出街冇咁迫<br />\n食野唔洗等位<br />\n有樓住<br />\n<br />\n根本香港頂盡500萬人就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f2ee3d28fa657cc255b1af39613ff3062741dd1","tid":657432,"uid":114275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T06:11:27.000Z","msg":"肯撚定 我支持你"},{"pid":"c53008c3627c02045e949b2eedf2d04e223721ef","tid":657432,"uid":442,"like":33,"dislike":2,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T06:11:54.000Z","msg":"當人口跌到呢個數既時候你應該會驚自己會係被消除既其中一個"},{"pid":"46903c84c90fd8b06f78850255aca580358a699f","tid":657432,"uid":176366,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T06:11:58.000Z","msg":"冇曬啲蝗同蝻根本天堂<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但現實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"360ce24b990eeac43c27aeb021f58e98c7e08c4c","tid":657432,"uid":139139,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T06:13:00.000Z","msg":"冇女人？"},{"pid":"ae8772aad99bec9f416d9d6f2e3e219581b77269","tid":657432,"uid":54551,"like":4,"dislike":17,"score":-13,"quote":{"pid":"46903c84c90fd8b06f7885